<baselayout title="Belt Conveyors: Types, Materials &#x26; Selection Guide | Packaging Conveyor" description="Guide to belt conveyor types: flat belt, cleated, modular plastic, wire mesh, and timing belts. Comparison, speed ranges, and selection criteria for packaging applications." canonical="https://packagingconveyor.com/conveyor-types/belt-conveyors/" schema="{[breadcrumbSchema," faqschema,="" articleschema]}="">

  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
  <nav class="bg-surface border-b border-border" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-3">
      <ol class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-ink-muted">
